=============== Ollama Embedding =======================
Ollama supports embedding models, making it possible to build RAG(Retrieval Augmented Generation) applications that combine text prompts with existing documents or other data.

Olama is kind of a platform where you will be able to use open source models like Llama3 , Phi3,Mistral, and Gemma.
These are various open source models that are available right now, and you can probably run all these models in your local machine itself in your local workstation.

Download Ollama for Windows
